          <p class='first-para'>
            I believe that the Minister used the expression, "environmental strategy", but it may be that again I did not hear her correctly. Did she say that?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-00843'>
        <a name='S5LV0664P0_20040719_GCR_96'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hollis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
