            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_32gc' title='Col. 32GC &mdash; HL Deb 19 July 2004 vol 664 c32GC' name='column_32gc' href='#column_32gc' rel='bookmark'>32GC</a>
            will probably be necessary to spell matters out because outside bodies have considerable interest in these matters. Given the Minister's assurance&#x2014;
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-00964'>
        <a name='S5LV0664P0_20040719_GCR_217'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hollis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
